</emphasis>
<collectingCountry box="[380,470,151,175]" name="Jamaica" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">Jamaica</collectingCountry>
and its satellite islands and Grand Cayman Island (
<figureCitation box="[1045,1129,151,175]" captionStart="FIGURE 26" captionStartId="44.[151,250,1106,1129]" captionTargetBox="[159,1427,275,1085]" captionTargetId="figure-388@44.[151,1436,267,1085]" captionTargetPageId="44" captionText="FIGURE 26. Distribution of the Norops sagrei and Norops valencienni Species Groups." pageId="44" pageNumber="45">Fig. 26</figureCitation>
